<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Needle (Q)</b></li><ul><li> The power ratio of this ability has been increased to 0.6, up from 0.5.</li></ul><li><b>Pure Blood (W)</b></li><ul><li> Consecutive blood orbs will now deal 60% damage, up from 35%.</li></ul><li><b>Exsanguinate (R)</b></li><ul><li> The range of this ability has been increased to 650, up from 575.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32.1 (July 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Needle (Q)</b></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been increased to 12/11/10/9/8, up from 11/10/9/8/7.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 31 (June 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Pure Blood (W)</B></li><ul><li>The blood orbs generated by this ability will now generate 1% faster per 1% cooldown reduction that Viyana has.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 30 (May 27th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Needle (Q)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where this Shaper could outrange her own heal.</li></ul><li><B>Pure Blood (W)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the tooltip for this ability was displaying the incorrect value for the base healing values.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 29 (May 5th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Exsanguinate (R)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the target would become immune to knockbacks during the duration of this ability.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 27 (March 17, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Needle (Q)</li><ul><li>The base healing done by this ability has been reduced to 40/55/70/85/100, down from 45/75/105/135/155.</li><li>The healing bonus Health ratio has been increased to 12% of bonus Health, up from 7.5%.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Needle (Q)<ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 800, from previous value of 835.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.5, down from 0.9.</li></ul><li>Pure Blood (W)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 775, from previous value of 850.</li></ul><li>Leech (E)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 575, from previous value of 625.</li><li>The Power ratio on this ability has been reduced to 0.5, down from 0.6</li></ul><li>Exsanguinate (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 575, from previous value of 625.</li><li>The base damage of this ability has been changed to 150/250/350, from 175/240/304.</li><li>The Power ratio for this ability has been reduced to 0.6, down from 0.8.</li></ul></ul>